  "keyFeatures": [
    "Reusable C++ base classes for Slot and Slingo game types",
    "MT19937-64 Mersenne Twister RNG with seed reproducibility",
    "Multiple win evaluation modes: Paylines, Ways, Scatter pays, Clusters, Megaways",
    "Monte Carlo simulation engine for RTP verification",
    "Configurable paytable, reel strips, and paylines via CSV files",
    "Win capping (variadic cap_wins) for regulatory compliance",
    "JSON output for simulation results and game configuration",
    "GitHub Actions workflow for template scaffolding into new projects",
    "Weighted random sampling with and without replacement",
    "Cascade mechanics and symbol multiplier support"
  ],
